{"lastModified":1775079307467,"uri":"c::28226710116::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Bahamas, Florida\n\nThe 2023 Azimut 68 Fly is a masterpiece of contemporary Italian yacht design, blending cutting-edge innovation, timeless elegance, and exhilarating performance. Like new and never chartered before, this yacht offers an unparalleled experience of luxury and comfort for discerning guests seeking the very best on the water.\n\nPowered by twin MAN engines and a powerful stabilizer, the 68 Fly delivers impressive power with effortless handling, ensuring a smooth and refined cruising experience whether gliding through Miami’s Intracoastal waterways or embarking on a multi-day escape to the Keys or the Bahamas.\n\nHer expansive flybridge is an entertainer’s dream, featuring a helm station, wet bar, al fresco dining area, and multiple sun loungers with panoramic ocean views, the perfect setting to relax under the Florida sun or toast the sunset with friends. The aft deck seamlessly connects indoor and outdoor living spaces, while the bow lounge with oversized sunpads invites moments of total relaxation and serenity at sea.\n\nInside, the 2023 model showcases Azimut’s latest interior design, with exquisite materials, ambient lighting, and an open layout that exudes modern sophistication. The salon is bright and spacious, framed by floor-to-ceiling windows that flood the space with natural light. A refined dining area and a fully equipped galley complement the contemporary setting, creating the ideal atmosphere for both entertaining and unwinding.\n\nBelow deck, she offers four luxurious staterooms — including a full-beam master suite with ensuite bathroom — providing exceptional comfort and privacy for overnight stays. Every detail has been meticulously designed to deliver an experience that is as stylish as it is serene.\n\nBlending Italian artistry with state-of-the-art technology, the 2023 Azimut 68 Fly stands as a symbol of elegance and exclusivity — the perfect yacht for those who demand excellence in every detail.\n\nSuggested Itinerary\n\nMorning: Depart from your preferred Miami marina and cruise along the scenic Intracoastal Waterway, passing Bal Harbour, Sunny Isles, and Golden Beach. Soak in the views from the flybridge or bow lounge as you glide through crystal waters.\n\nMidday: Drop anchor at the famous Haulover Sandbar, a local favorite for swimming, sunbathing, and enjoying the warm Miami waters.\n\nAfternoon: Continue to Oleta River State Park for a peaceful break surrounded by nature. Enjoy lunch onboard or explore mangrove-lined channels before cruising back toward the city as the sun begins to set.\n\nEvening: Celebrate golden hour from the flybridge or aft deck with a chilled drink in hand as Miami’s skyline lights up the horizon — the perfect ending to a perfect day.","blueprint":{"name":"SPYSEA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::01635e80-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::010279d0-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::014b42a0-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::01031610-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::01070db0-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::014d1760-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::0105fc40-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e06b9bf0-b499-11f0-8221-31ce60d59e1a::assets::015024a0-b49d-11f0-92c8-938eb55b00ef/{imageVariant}","/m